Author: sunsetlover19
Text: Sometimes relapses do occur despite a time length of not having disordered thoughts or behaviors. From the sounds of it, what has been happening with you the last month does grant concern. I urge you to seek immediate help for yourself because I don't want this to progress for you or have a place back in your life. What's going on with you doesn't mean you are hopeless or will experience issues again later in life and even if you did, you've already fought this and conquered it in the past. Therefore, I believe you could get through it again. Please try to take care of yourself and consider reaching out to someone for professional help
